chat_messages.text:
 Wah bagus, kamu udah explore Shopee Open Platform! 👍

Saya cek dokumentasi yang kamu share, dan saya punya **good news & bad news**:

---

## **📋 Shopee Open Platform - Realita untuk Indonesia**

### **❌ BAD NEWS:**

**Shopee Open Platform (API Official) untuk Indonesia:**

1. **Bukan untuk Affiliate Program** ❌
   - API ini khusus untuk **Sellers/Merchants** (penjual)
   - Bukan untuk affiliate marketers
   - Fokus ke: inventory management, order processing, logistics

2. **Akses Terbatas** ❌
   - Harus **registered merchant** di Shopee
   - Perlu approval dari Shopee (proses panjang)
   - Untuk business use only (toko resmi)

3. **Tidak Ada Public Product Search API** ❌
   - Ga bisa search produk orang lain
   - Ga bisa akses review/rating produk lain
   - Ga bisa akses flash sale public
   - Hanya bisa manage produk **toko kamu sendiri**

4. **Region Support:**
   ```
   ✅ Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Vietnam, Philippines, Taiwan
   ✅ Indonesia (TAPI terbatas!)

   Indonesia support API-nya lebih sedikit dibanding negara lain
   ```

---

### **✅ GOOD NEWS:**

**Kamu TETAP bisa ambil data Shopee dengan cara lain!**

---

## **🔧 SOLUSI: Web Scraping (Best Approach)**

Karena **official API tidak cocok untuk affiliate**, solusi terbaik adalah **web scraping**.

### **Data yang Bisa Diambil via Scraping:**

```
✅ Product Info:
   - Nama produk
   - Harga (normal & diskon)
   - Rating & jumlah review
   - Sold count (jumlah terjual)
   - Stock status
   - Product images (multiple)
   - Product description
   - Category & tags
   - Seller info

✅ Reviews/Comments:
   - Review text
   - Rating (1-5 stars)
   - Reviewer name
   - Verified purchase badge
   - Review images
   - Review date
   - Helpful count

✅ Flash Sale Info:
   - Flash sale badge
   - Original price
   - Discount percentage
   - Time remaining (countdown)
   - Stock remaining

✅ Recommendations:
   - "Produk Serupa"
   - "Mungkin Kamu Suka"
   - Category best sellers

✅ Shop Info:
   - Shop name
   - Shop rating
   - Product count
   - Follower count
```

---

## **💻 CARA SCRAPING SHOPEE - Complete Guide**

### **Method 1: Puppeteer (Recommended for Dynamic Content)**

Shopee pakai **React/JavaScript** untuk render halaman, jadi butuh browser automation.

```javascript
// scraper/shopee-scraper.js
import puppeteer from 'puppeteer';

export async function scrapeShopeeProduct(productUrl) {
  const browser = await puppeteer.launch({
    headless: true,
    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-setuid-sandbox']
  });

  const page = await browser.newPage();

  // Set user agent (penting biar ga ke-detect sebagai bot)
  await page.setUserAgent(
    'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36'
  );

  try {
    // Go to product page
    await page.goto(productUrl, { 
      waitUntil: 'networkidle2',
      timeout: 30000 
    });

    // Wait for content to load
    await page.waitForSelector('[data-testid="product-name"]', { timeout: 10000 });

    // Extract data
    const productData = await page.evaluate(() => {
      // Helper function to safely get text
      const getText = (selector) => {
        const el = document.querySelector(selector);
        return el ? el.innerText.trim() : null;
      };

      // Helper function to get attribute
      const getAttr = (selector, attr) => {
        const el = document.querySelector(selector);
        return el ? el.getAttribute(attr) : null;
      };

      return {
        // Basic Info
        name: getText('[data-testid="product-name"]'),
        price: getText('.pqTWkA'), // Price selector (may change)
        originalPrice: getText('.mYiC94'), // Original price
        discount: getText('.percent'), // Discount %

        // Stats
        rating: getText('.review-rating'),
        reviewCount: getText('.review-count'),
        soldCount: getText('.sold-count'),

        // Images
        images: Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.product-image img'))
          .map(img => img.src),

        // Description
        description: getText('.product-description'),

        // Category & Tags
        category: getText('.breadcrumb'),

        // Shop Info
        shopName: getText('.shop-name'),
        shopRating: getText('.shop-rating'),

        // Flash Sale Info (if exists)
        isFlashSale: !!document.querySelector('.flash-sale-badge'),
        flashSaleEndTime: getAttr('.flash-sale-timer', 'data-end-time'),
      };
    });

    await browser.close();
    return productData;

  } catch (error) {
    await browser.close();
    throw new Error(`Scraping failed: ${error.message}`);
  }
}
```

---

### **Method 2: Scrape Reviews/Comments**

```javascript
export async function scrapeShopeeReviews(productUrl, maxReviews = 50) {
  const browser = await puppeteer.launch({ headless: true });
  const page = await browser.newPage();

  await page.setUserAgent('Mozilla/5.0...');
  await page.goto(productUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle2' });

  // Scroll to reviews section
  await page.evaluate(() => {
    document.querySelector('.product-reviews')?.scrollIntoView();
  });

  await page.waitForSelector('.product-review-item', { timeout: 5000 });

  // Load more reviews (click "Lihat Selengkapnya" button)
  let reviewCount = 0;
  while (reviewCount < maxReviews) {
    const loadMoreBtn = await page.$('.load-more-reviews');
    if (!loadMoreBtn) break;

    await loadMoreBtn.click();
    await page.waitForTimeout(1000); // Wait for new reviews to load

    const currentCount = await page.$$eval('.product-review-item', items => items.length);
    if (currentCount === reviewCount) break; // No more reviews
    reviewCount = currentCount;
  }

  // Extract reviews
  const reviews = await page.evaluate(() => {
    return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.product-review-item'))
      .map(item => {
        const getText = (selector) => {
          const el = item.querySelector(selector);
          return el ? el.innerText.trim() : null;
        };

        return {
          rating: item.querySelectorAll('.star-icon.filled').length,
          text: getText('.review-text'),
          author: getText('.review-author'),
          date: getText('.review-date'),
          isVerified: !!item.querySelector('.verified-badge'),
          helpful: getText('.helpful-count'),
          images: Array.from(item.querySelectorAll('.review-image img'))
            .map(img => img.src)
        };
      });
  });

  await browser.close();
  return reviews;
}
```

---

### **Method 3: Scrape Flash Sale Products**

```javascript
export async function scrapeFlashSale() {
  const browser = await puppeteer.launch({ headless: true });
  const page = await browser.newPage();

  await page.setUserAgent('Mozilla/5.0...');

  // Go to Flash Sale page
  await page.goto('https://shopee.co.id/flash_sale', { 
    waitUntil: 'networkidle2' 
  });

  await page.waitForSelector('.flash-sale-item', { timeout: 10000 });

  const flashSaleProducts = await page.evaluate(() => {
    return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.flash-sale-item'))
      .map(item => {
        const getText = (selector) => {
          const el = item.querySelector(selector);
          return el ? el.innerText.trim() : null;
        };

        return {
          name: getText('.product-name'),
          price: getText('.flash-sale-price'),
          originalPrice: getText('.original-price'),
          discount: getText('.discount-label'),
          image: item.querySelector('img')?.src,
          productUrl: item.querySelector('a')?.href,
          soldPercentage: getText('.sold-percentage'),
          timeRemaining: getText('.time-remaining')
        };
      });
  });

  await browser.close();
  return flashSaleProducts;
}
```

---

### **Method 4: Scrape Recommendations**

```javascript
export async function scrapeRecommendations(productUrl) {
  const browser = await puppeteer.launch({ headless: true });
  const page = await browser.newPage();

  await page.setUserAgent('Mozilla/5.0...');
  await page.goto(productUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle2' });

  // Scroll to recommendations section
  await page.evaluate(() => {
    document.querySelector('.recommendation-section')?.scrollIntoView();
  });

  await page.waitForSelector('.recommendation-item', { timeout: 5000 });

  const recommendations = await page.evaluate(() => {
    return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.recommendation-item'))
      .slice(0, 10) // Ambil 10 produk pertama
      .map(item => ({
        name: item.querySelector('.product-name')?.innerText,
        price: item.querySelector('.price')?.innerText,
        rating: item.querySelector('.rating')?.innerText,
        sold: item.querySelector('.sold-count')?.innerText,
        image: item.querySelector('img')?.src,
        url: item.querySelector('a')?.href
      }));
  });

  await browser.close();
  return recommendations;
}
```

---

## **⚠️ CHALLENGES & SOLUTIONS**

### **Challenge 1: Selector Berubah**
```
Problem: Shopee sering update class names/selectors

Solution:
✅ Gunakan multiple selectors (fallback)
✅ Gunakan data attributes jika ada
✅ Regex pattern untuk extract data dari script tags
✅ Regular maintenance (update selectors)
```

**Example dengan Fallback:**
```javascript
const getPrice = () => {
  const selectors = [
    '.pqTWkA',           // Selector terbaru
    '.product-price',    // Fallback 1
    '[class*="price"]'   // Fallback 2
  ];

  for (const selector of selectors) {
    const el = document.querySelector(selector);
    if (el) return el.innerText;
  }
  return null;
};
```

---

### **Challenge 2: Anti-Bot Detection**
```
Problem: Shopee detect bot & block scraping

Solutions:
✅ User Agent rotation
✅ Random delays (jangan terlalu cepat)
✅ Use residential proxies (optional)
✅ Cookie management
✅ Headless: false (untuk testing)
```

**Example:**
```javascript
// Random delay
const randomDelay = (min, max) => {
  return new Promise(resolve => {
    const delay = Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min + 1)) + min;
    setTimeout(resolve, delay);
  });
};

// Usage
await page.goto(url);
await randomDelay(2000, 5000); // Random 2-5 detik
await page.click('.load-more');
```

---

### **Challenge 3: Dynamic Content Loading**
```
Problem: Data load via AJAX/API calls

Solution:
✅ Intercept network requests
✅ Wait for specific API calls
✅ Extract data dari __NEXT_DATA__ (if available)
```

**Example - Intercept API:**
```javascript
const page = await browser.newPage();

// Listen to API responses
page.on('response', async (response) => {
  const url = response.url();

  // Check if it's product API
  if (url.includes('/api/v4/item/get')) {
    const data = await response.json();
    console.log('Product data from API:', data);
  }

  // Check if it's review API
  if (url.includes('/api/v2/item/get_ratings')) {
    const reviews = await response.json();
    console.log('Reviews from API:', reviews);
  }
});

await page.goto(productUrl);
```

---

### **Challenge 4: Rate Limiting**
```
Problem: Terlalu banyak request → IP di-ban

Solution:
✅ Queue system (batch processing)
✅ Delay between requests (5-10 detik)
✅ Rotating proxies (untuk scale besar)
✅ Cache results (jangan scrape berkali-kali)
```

**Example dengan Queue:**
```javascript
import PQueue from 'p-queue';

const queue = new PQueue({
  concurrency: 1,      // 1 request at a time
  interval: 10000,     // 10 second interval
  intervalCap: 1       // 1 request per interval
});

// Add scraping jobs to queue
const products = ['url1', 'url2', 'url3'];

const results = await Promise.all(
  products.map(url => 
    queue.add(() => scrapeShopeeProduct(url))
  )
);
```

---

## **🏗️ ARCHITECTURE untuk Scraping System**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│     Firebase Functions              │
│     (Scheduled Cloud Functions)     │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                     │
│  1. Daily Scrape Job (12 AM)       │
│     → Scrape new products           │
│     → Update existing products      │
│     → Check price changes           │
│                                     │
│  2. Review Scrape Job (Weekly)     │
│     → Update reviews for top 50    │
│     → Re-analyze with AI            │
│                                     │
│  3. Flash Sale Monitor (Hourly)    │
│     → Check flash sale products    │
│     → Auto-generate tweets         │
│                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
           ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│     Firestore Database              │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Collections:                       │
│  • products                         │
│  • reviews                          │
│  • flash_sales                      │
│  • scrape_logs                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## **📦 PACKAGE RECOMMENDATIONS**

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "puppeteer": "^21.0.0",           // Browser automation
    "puppeteer-extra": "^3.3.6",      // Extra plugins
    "puppeteer-extra-plugin-stealth": "^2.11.2", // Anti-detection
    "cheerio": "^1.0.0-rc.12",        // HTML parsing (faster)
    "axios": "^1.6.0",                // HTTP requests
    "p-queue": "^7.4.1",              // Queue management
    "user-agents": "^1.1.0"           // Random user agents
  }
}
```

**Setup with Stealth Plugin:**
```javascript
import puppeteer from 'puppeteer-extra';
import StealthPlugin from 'puppeteer-extra-plugin-stealth';

// Add stealth plugin (bypass bot detection)
puppeteer.use(StealthPlugin());

const browser = await puppeteer.launch({
  headless: true,
  args: [
    '--no-sandbox',
    '--disable-setuid-sandbox',
    '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'
  ]
});
```

---

## **💡 ALTERNATIVE: Use Existing APIs (Unofficial)**

Ada beberapa **third-party services** yang mungkin bisa bantu:

1. **ScraperAPI** (https://www.scraperapi.com/)
   - Proxy rotation built-in
   - Handle anti-bot protection
   - Paid service (~$49/month)

2. **Oxylabs** (https://oxylabs.io/)
   - E-commerce scraping specialist
   - Lebih mahal (~$99/month)

3. **Bright Data** (https://brightdata.com/)
   - Enterprise-grade
   - Very expensive

**Tapi untuk project kamu, saya recommend buat sendiri aja pakai Puppeteer!** (gratis & lebih flexible)

---

## **🎯 FINAL RECOMMENDATION**

**Tech Stack untuk Scraping:**
```
Puppeteer + Stealth Plugin (scraping)
    ↓
Firebase Functions (scheduled jobs)
    ↓
Firestore (store data)
    ↓
Gemini AI (analyze reviews)
    ↓
Next.js Frontend (display data)
```

**Data Update Strategy:**
```
• New products: Manual add (via admin dashboard)
• Existing products: Auto-update daily (price, stock, sold)
• Reviews: Scrape on-demand (when product added)
• Flash sales: Auto-scrape every hour
```

---

**Mau saya buatkan prototype scraper-nya sekarang?** 

Bisa saya bikinin:
1. **Complete Shopee Scraper** (product, reviews, flash sale)
2. **Firebase Functions** untuk scheduled scraping
3. **Admin dashboard** untuk manage scraping jobs
4. **Error handling & retry logic**

Siap? 🚀

